## 5. Business Deployment Paradigms

| Paradigm | Description | Example |
|----------|-------------|---------|
| **SaaS** | Hosted service, user pays subscription | ChatGPT Plus |
| **MaaS** (Model-as-a-Service) | Expose model via API, pay per token | OpenAI API, Anthropic API |
| **DaaS** (Data-as-a-Service) | Monetise processed data/insights | Bloomberg Terminal AI |
| **RaaS** (Results-as-a-Service) | Deliver outputs/decisions, not models | AI-generated reports |

